<item>
            <title>[STR-3174] ComposableRequestProcessor.process() should invoke Context&apos;s release() method inside a finally clause</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/STR-3174</link>
                <project id="12311043" key="STR">Struts 1</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The process method in org.apache.struts.chain.ComposableRequestProcessor invokes release() on the ActionContext only on success.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The release() method should be invoked regardless of the result of the execution. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To fix, simply add a finally clause around the line like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;finally {&lt;br/&gt;
    context.release();&lt;br/&gt;
}&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
